snippet.title: Cosmic Top Secret - Announcement Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: The award-winning Cosmic Top Secret launches on May 21! Help Trine discover the truth about her parent's work during the Cold War. Was her Dad a spy? Did he save the world from a nuclear war? Dive into historical plots through an unique and emotionally-engaging adventure.
